PM-KISAN (Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi): Provides income support of Rs 6000/year to all landholding farmer families. Amount released in 3 equal installments of Rs 2000 each. Eligibility: Farmer families with cultivable land. Exclusions: Income tax payers, professionals, retired government employees. Application: PM-KISAN portal or CSC centers. Documents: Aadhaar, bank account, land records.˙˙